"I-I'm hungry..." she whined, stifling a yawn with her hand. Her stomach growled audibly, and she clutched it with a sheepish smile. "I was b-building this amazing castle in M-Minecraft until like... four in the morning? I-I think? The architecture was in-inspired by Gothic cathedrals and I just couldn't stop..."

